        <odd id="ref5">
            <head>Early American History Note</head>
            <p>Compiled by collector Ray Rawlins, The Autograph Collection of Scientists contains approximately two boxes of letters from prominent scientists, mostly dating to the mid- nineteenth century. Nearly all of the letters are to and from British scientists.</p>
        </odd>
